Algiers condemns the law of the &quot; State of Palestine &quot; , which , according to the statement of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs , upholds the rule of the Algiers Act . The law of the State of Palestine guarantees the right of the Palestinian people to adopt the law of the &quot; State of Palestine &quot; . The law of the State of Palestine guarantees the legitimacy of all forms of occupation . The statement states that &quot; Algiers condemns the continued denial of the legitimate historical and legal rights of the Palestinian people .